    i.fa.fa-sun-o.fa-spin
section#services
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-4.text-center.padding.wow.fadeIn[data-wow-duration="1000ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"]
        .single-service
          .wow.scaleIn[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"]
            img[src="/assets/triangle/services/1.png" alt=""]
          h2
            | It all starts with you...
          p
            | You tell us about the perfect new toy you just got for your child.
      .col-sm-4.text-center.padding.wow.fadeIn[data-wow-duration="1000ms" data-wow-delay="600ms"]
        .single-service
          .wow.scaleIn[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="600ms"]
            img[src="/assets/triangle/home/icon1.png" alt=""]
          h2
            | ... we constantly monitor toys...
          p
            | We go through millions of reports of toy recalls, safety warnings and stories of problematic toys.
      .col-sm-4.text-center.padding.wow.fadeIn[data-wow-duration="1000ms" data-wow-delay="900ms"]
        .single-service
          .wow.scaleIn[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="900ms"]
            img[src="/assets/triangle/home/cycle.png" alt=""]
          h2
            | ... you get immediate alerts
          p
            | When a safety issue is raised on one of your kid toys we send you immediate alerts to make sure you are in the known.
section#action.responsive
  .vertical-center
    .container
      .row
        .action.take-tour
          .col-sm-7.wow.fadeInLeft[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"]
            h1.title
              | We track toys and make sure they are safe
            p
              | Did you know that in 2013 alone one toy was recalled every three days?
          .col-sm-5.text-center.wow.fadeInRight[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"]
            .tour-button
              a.btn.btn-highlight.btn-common[href=new_user_registration_path] Start Now, It's Free!
section#features
  .container
    .row
      .single-features
        .col-sm-5.wow.fadeInLeft[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"]
          img.img-responsive[src="/assets/triangle/home/image1.png" alt=""]
        .col-sm-6.wow.fadeInRight[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"]
          h2 Catch unsafe toys easily
          p
            | Getting rid of unsafe toys is ridiculously easy now, we'll tell you exactly what toy can be a hazard for your kids.
      .single-features
        .col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-1.align-right.wow.fadeInLeft[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"]
          h2
            | No credit card required! Instant protection!
          p
            | We don't believe in artificial pay-walls, we believe in getting you the most reliable protection from hazardous toys as fast as possible.
          p
            a.btn.btn-common[href=new_user_registration_path] Get Started Now
        .col-sm-5.wow.fadeInRight[data-wow-duration="500ms" data-wow-delay="300ms"]
          img.img-responsive[src="/assets/triangle/home/image3.png" alt=""]

